arStrings.szText: A small piece of scribbled parchment
Written by a monk of the Orbei Monastery, in an hasty scribble.

(PH) "Something isn't right, the Abbot has allowed the stranger into the Inner Cloister. He told him the words of our founders! I heard him! Take this note to Monk Lahya and..." The note ends with a scrawl and bloodstains.
